---
// Hero — dark gradient with teal accents
---

<section class="hero-gradient py-32 md:py-48">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 md:px-8 text-center">
    <!-- Pre-heading badge -->
    <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-teal-500/10 px-3 py-1 text-[13px] font-bold tracking-widest text-foggy-teal">
      LOCAL AI INFRASTRUCTURE
    </span>

    <h1 class="mt-6 font-bold tracking-tight text-white" style="font-size: clamp(40px, 6vw, 72px); line-height: 1.1;">
      AI inference, run locally,<br class="hidden sm:block" /> in your country.
    </h1>

    <p class="mx-auto mt-6 max-w-2xl text-[20px] leading-relaxed text-foggy-text-on-dark">
      Foggy turns the desktops and laptops already sitting inside banks, hospitals, ministries, and universities in East Africa into a usable AI compute fleet. Same models the hyperscalers run, 60–80% cheaper, in your own building, in your own languages.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap items-center justify-center gap-4">
      <a href="#cta" class="rounded-lg bg-foggy-teal px-5 py-3 font-bold text-white hover:bg-foggy-teal-dark transition-colors">
        Request a pilot
      </a>
      <a href="#evidence" class="rounded-lg border border-slate-600 px-5 py-3 font-bold text-white hover:bg-white/5 transition-colors">
        See it run
      </a>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-8 text-[14px] italic text-foggy-text-muted-dark">
      First pilot deploys May 2026 at JKUAT, Nairobi &middot; Active conversations with Safaricom and MINICT Rwanda &middot; YC S26 applicant
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Section divider glow -->
  <div class="section-divider-glow mt-16 mx-auto max-w-4xl"></div>
</section>
